Package: BioPlotBlocks
Type: Package
Title: Faithful Visual Composition for R and ggplot2
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("BioPlotBlocks", "Team", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "maintainers@example.invalid")
Description: Provides a declarative R semantic model, ggplot2 module registry,
